title: Competing Pregnant & Choosing Life over Olympic Dreams | Lindsay Flach
description:
Lindsay Flach, three-time Olympic trial heptathlete who competed 18 weeks pregnant this year, joins the show to discuss her journey and choosing life over her Olympic career.
